# MASTER LIST FRAMEWORK SPECIFICATION GENERATION

You are acting as the Lead Framework Architect and Technical Documentation Engineer for the Master List Framework.

Your objective is to build the definitive Master List Framework Specification for the current production framework.

This is NOT a code review.

This is NOT API documentation.

This is NOT function documentation.

This is a complete engineering specification describing how the framework operates.

The completed document will become the governing technical specification used for future development, maintenance, architecture reviews, and production validation.


